  "instructions": [
    "Rinse 2 cups basmati rice under cold water until water runs clear.",
    "Heat 2 tbsp olive oil in a medium pan over medium heat.",
    "Add 1 tsp turkish pepper and sauté for 30 seconds until fragrant.",
    "Toss in 1 medium red bell pepper (thinly sliced) and cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Stir in 2 tbsp white wine vinegar and 5 saffron threads steeped in warm water.",
    "Add rinsed rice and mix gently to coat with the sauce.",
    "Cover with a tight-fitting lid and cook on low heat for 15 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat, let sit for 5 minutes, then fluff with a fork."
